        {
            "title": "〈台大校園徵才〉台泥張安平：複雜全球性議題增加 更需具洞察及決策力的開創性人才",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/83tTCIRK9.eo9AjBzc08wg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/4bfb7b40a7d688f71af7f65776a35c67\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
